Company Overview of Hudson Valley Property Group LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Hudson Valley Property Group LLC engages in the development and preservation of affordable and mixed-income housing properties in the United States. The company also engages in the acquisition and rehabilitation of existing properties. It acquires HUD assisted, tax credit, and affordable market rate properties. In addition, the company helps not-for profit organizations to rehabilitate and preserve their affordable housing assets. Hudson Valley Property Group LLC was founded in 2010 and is based in New York, New York.


394 BroadwaySuite 405New York, NY 10013United StatesFounded in 2010



Phone: 917-398-4100

